Sage Group Mulls Sale of Healthcare Division, Sunday Times Says

-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 
2011-05-29T10:34:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/sage-group-mulls-sale-of-healthcare-division-sunday-times-says.html
Sage Group Plc (SGE) , a U.K. software
maker, has begun a review of its healthcare division which may
lead to a sale of the unit, the  Sunday Times  reported, without
saying where it got the information.  Sage will make a decision this summer and has not yet hired
an investment bank to advise it, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
 gfinch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Evans at 
 eevans3@bloomberg.net  